{"id":"a020","internalId":"d0c3b16e-6bd4-40ef-838a-1e60c51d46d8","createdAt":"2026-01-28T06:53:20.243Z","updatedAt":"2026-03-24T10:39:59.884Z","status":{"code":"PUBLISHED","name":"Published"},"assessmentType":{"code":"CAR_ASSISTED_DRIVING","name":"Car Assisted Driving"},"assessmentDiagrams":[],"publicationDate":"2024-10-23","publicationYear":"2024","ratingYear":2024,"SPRefNumber":"a020","umbracoRefNumber":null,"rescueSheetURL":null,"greenNcapURL":null,"frontalImageURL":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/d0c3b16e-6bd4-40ef-838a-1e60c51d46d8/BMW-i5__7229e0822cbe72f4_original.png","frontalImage":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/d0c3b16e-6bd4-40ef-838a-1e60c51d46d8/BMW-i5__7229e0822cbe72f4_original.png","altText":null,"width":1144,"height":760,"formats":{"large":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/d0c3b16e-6bd4-40ef-838a-1e60c51d46d8/BMW-i5__28524dc44d4f74be_lg.webp","width":1144,"height":760},"small":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/d0c3b16e-6bd4-40ef-838a-1e60c51d46d8/BMW-i5__e164be5df8286489_sm.webp","width":320,"height":213},"medium":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/d0c3b16e-6bd4-40ef-838a-1e60c51d46d8/BMW-i5__258202314080e904_md.webp","width":768,"height":510},"xlarge":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/d0c3b16e-6bd4-40ef-838a-1e60c51d46d8/BMW-i5__28524dc44d4f74be_xl.webp","width":1144,"height":760},"thumbnail":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/d0c3b16e-6bd4-40ef-838a-1e60c51d46d8/BMW-i5__6582c368f6bab2bc_thumb.webp","width":156,"height":104}}},"newsMarketURL":"https://news.euroncap.com/safercars/choose-a-car/bmw-i5---euro-ncap-2024-assisted-driving-results---very-good-grading/s/f374c826-2188-45c5-93f3-2479255da3d7","resultApplicability":"all","comments":"<p>BMW’s appropriately named Driving Assistant Professional’ accurately portrays system functionality. The promotional material and the handbook correctly indicate the limitations of the system capabilities. System status information is clearly displayed in the driver’s direct line of sight by a head-up display. The i5 monitors that the driver’s hands are on the steering wheel. The car’s direct driver monitoring system is used only to ensure the driver is not incapacitated. The system balances driver steering input with lane guidance, promoting co-operative driving.</p><p>The i5 combines map-based speed limit information with real time camera inputs to manage fixed, variable and temporary speed limit signs. However, the system does not adapt speed for upcoming road features such as curves and junctions. The car responds to avoid or mitigate a collision in all of the test scenarios for automatic cruise control. The driver is supported through the S-Bend, staying within the lane at all test speeds. The BMW has a lane change assist feature. In the case of an unresponsive driver, the i5 performs a controlled stop within its lane. If the radar or camera is blocked the i5 provides a timely warning and prevents system activation.</p><p>The i5 from BMW balances a high level of Vehicle Assistance with a similar level of Driver Engagement. Combined with excellent safety back-up, the system, overall, offers Very Good highway assistance.</p>","testedHandOfDrive":null,"assessmentTags":[],"assessmentData":{"carAssistedDriving":{"disclaimer":"When using Assisted Driving Systems (also known as SAE Level 2 systems), a driver’s responsibilities include monitoring the system’s control of speed, braking and steering at all times, strict compliance with traffic rules, and maintaining situational awareness throughout the journey. Certain situations might negatively influence the system’s performance (e.g. poor weather, faded lane markings, construction zones, exiting a tunnel), resulting in a sudden interruption of the lateral and/or longitudinal support (system disengagement). Moreover, the system may fail to detect certain road users such as motorcyclists not directly in front of the vehicle, or stationary objects. Appropriate fitness to drive is critical for safe travel, even when using Assisted Driving Systems. Visual distraction (e.g. eyes off the road), impairment (e.g. drowsiness, intoxication) as well as unresponsiveness, poses high risks. It is highly recommended to keep your hands on the steering wheel at all times to ensure immediate reaction when the system disengages.","domain":{"highway":"RECOMMENDED","interUrban":"RECOMMENDED","urban":"NOT_RECOMMENDED"},"nicePublicationDate":"October 2024","assistedDrivingPerformance":{"assistanceCompetence":{"score":76,"maxScore":100,"normalisedScore":76,"driverEngagement":{"score":76,"maxScore":100,"normalisedScore":76,"elements":{"consumerInformation":{"score":23,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"GREEN","elements":{"marketingMaterial":{"url":"https://www.bmw.co.uk/en/shop/ls/dp/DrivingAssistant_Plus_SFA_gb","viewDate":"15/10/2024"},"quickStartGuide":true,"handbook":{"url":"https://euroncap.blob.core.windows.net/media/83333/bmw-i5-2024-a020_vehicle-handbook_driver-assistance-systems.pdf"}}},"systemStatus":{"score":25,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"GREEN","elements":{"continuousSystemStatusIndicator":"GREEN","systemStatusChangeIndicator":"GREEN"}},"driverMonitoring":{"score":5,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"BROWN","elements":{"handsOnMonitoring":"GREEN","directDriverMonitoring":"RED"}},"drivingCollaboration":{"score":23,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"GREEN","elements":{"increaseSteeringTorque":"YELLOW","overrideResponse":"GREEN","comment":"System continues to assist while driver steers to avoid obstacle"}}}},"vehicleAssistance":{"score":83,"maxScore":100,"normalisedScore":83,"elements":{"speedAssistance":{"score":19.4,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"GREEN","elements":{"speedAssistSystems":{"responseToFixedSpeedLimit":"At speed at sign","responseToVariableSpeedLimit":"At speed at sign"},"speedLimitInfoFunction":{"generalRequirements":"Compliant","conditionalSpeedLimits":"GREEN","roadFeatures":"GREEN","localHazards":"RED","systemUpdates":"None"}}},"adaptiveCruiseControlPerformance":{"score":28.6,"maxScore":40,"verdict":"YELLOW","elements":{"scenarios":{"approachingStationaryTarget":{"car":"YELLOW","motorCycle":"YELLOW"},"approachingSlowerMovingTarget":{"car":"GREEN","motorCycle":"GREEN"},"approachingBrakingTarget":{"car":"YELLOW","motorCycle":"YELLOW"},"targetCuttingInFront":{"car":"GREEN","motorCycle":"GREEN"},"carCuttingOutFrontToExposeTarget":{"car":"GREEN","motorCycle":"GREEN"}},"undertakePrevention":{"undertakePreventionSpeedOver90km":"RED"},"adaptiveCruiseControlAutoResume":{"assistanceMaintainedAfterFullStop":"GREEN","systemAssistanceMaintained":"Automatic resume within 5s of stop and driver input required over 5s"}}},"steeringAssistance":{"score":35,"maxScore":35,"verdict":"GREEN","laneChangeAssist":true,"scenarios":{"80km":{"verdict":"GREEN","comment":"Vehicle stays in lane"},"100km":{"verdict":"GREEN","comment":"Vehicle stays in lane"},"120km":{"verdict":"GREEN","comment":"Vehicle stays in lane"}}}}}},"safetyBackup":{"score":90,"normalisedScore":90,"elements":{"systemFailure":{"score":23.3,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"GREEN","scenarios":{"sensorBlockedAtStartup":{"camera":{"engagement":"Full blockage after a 5 minute drive","warning":"Yes after sensor blocking"},"radar":{"engagement":"Partial blockage after a 5 minute drive","warning":"Yes after sensor blocking"}},"sensorBlockedVehicleMovingSystemInactive":{"camera":{"engagement":"Full blockage after a 5 minute drive","warning":"Yes after sensor blocking"},"radar":{"engagement":"After a 5 minute drive","warning":"After sensor blocking"}},"sensorBlockedVehicleMovingSystemActive":{"camera":{"engagement":"Full blockage within 2 minutes after blocking","warning":"Unknown (no OEM data) after sensor blocking"},"radar":{"engagement":"Partial blockage after sensor blocking","warning":"Unknown (no OEM data) after sensor blocking"}}}},"unresponsiveDriverIntervention":{"score":20,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"GREEN"},"collisionAvoidance":{"score":47.6,"maxScore":50,"verdict":"GREEN","scenarios":{"approachingStationaryTarget":{"car":"GREEN","motorcycle":"YELLOW"},"approachingSlowerMovingTarget":{"car":"GREEN","motorcycle":"GREEN"},"approachingBrakingTarget":{"car":"YELLOW","motorcycle":"YELLOW"},"targetCuttingInFront":{"car":"YELLOW","motorcycle":"GREEN"},"carCuttingOutInFrontToExposeTarget":{"car":"GREEN","motorcycle":"GREEN"},"approachingTargetAlongRoadside":{"vulnerableRoadUser":"GREEN"}}}}}}}},"carSafety":null,"carAssistedDriving":{"assistedDrivingGrading":{"code":"VERY_GOOD","name":"Very good"},"assistedDrivingPackName":"Driving Assistant Professional","safetyAssessmentId":"1032","assessmentReviews":[]},"truckSafety":null,"vanSafety":null,"model":{"id":"6de08499-0aeb-462d-a394-d690a92e0f82","createdAt":"2026-01-21T19:16:07.188215+00:00","updatedAt":"2026-01-21T19:16:07.188215+00:00","code":"BMW_5_SERIES","name":"5 Series","class":{"code":"LARGE_FAMILY_CAR","name":"Large Family Car"},"vehicleType":{"code":"CAR","name":"Car"}},"make":{"id":"ba362222-b63f-4da0-b451-7113f302e941","createdAt":"2026-01-21T19:13:43.112841+00:00","updatedAt":"2026-03-19T12:55:50.063123+00:00","code":"BMW","name":"BMW","logoPath":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/make-logo/BMW_logo__b5b007714d04a7c2_original.svg","negLogoPath":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/make-logo/BMW_negLogo__ff5a984a64f3914f_original.svg","logo":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/make-logo/BMW_logo__b5b007714d04a7c2_original.svg","width":null,"height":null,"formats":null},"negativeLogo":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/make-logo/BMW_negLogo__ff5a984a64f3914f_original.svg","width":null,"height":null,"formats":null}},"assessmentMedia":[{"id":"bc59ea2f-8c44-4ae7-94cc-be7d1aa2563f","createdAt":"2026-03-24T10:40:38.399021+00:00","updatedAt":"2026-03-24T10:40:38.399021+00:00","mediaType":"IMAGE","url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/d0c3b16e-6bd4-40ef-8